OL,3,CMark Carney to return 'home' in Mayo
OL,4,Cvisit
OL,6,FCanadian Prime Minister Mark Carney
OL,7,Fwill travel to the home county of his
OL,8,FIrish grandparents on Sunday.
OL,10,FMr Carney will fly to Co Mayo this
OL,11,Fmorning after spending Saturday in
OL,12,FDublin city.
OL,14,FHe traces his heritage back to
OL,15,FAughagower and will also spend much of
OL,16,Fthe day in the seaside town of
OL,17,FWestport.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
