FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781408877
OL,3,CMark Carney to return 'home' in Mayo
OL,4,Cvisit
OL,6,FHis itinerary includes a visit with
OL,7,FIrish President Catherine Connolly and
OL,8,Fengagements with Taoiseach Micheal
OL,9,FMartin.
OL,11,FMr Carney is the grandson of Irish
OL,12,Femigrants who were born in Mayo and
OL,13,Fleft the country more than 100 years
OL,14,Fago for Canada.
OL,26,@pD@arp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
